as the beginning that leads to 
the birth of an excellent child.

00:02:30.330 --> 00:02:32.040
Now, choose.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.920
Babyhead!

00:02:37.920 --> 00:02:39.790
H-H-Help me!

00:02:40.150 --> 00:02:41.140
Help me!

