They're starting to learn from their mother.

00:07:16.410 --> 00:07:18.580
Babyhead's child, that is...

00:07:18.580 --> 00:07:19.970
And this is great!

00:07:19.970 --> 00:07:23.260
They're already responding to their 
mother's desire to kill someone!

00:07:23.260 --> 00:07:25.670
Make us proud!

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:30.700
I'm telling you, some creepy bastard 
attacked me here! He attacked <i>me</i>!

00:07:30.700 --> 00:07:33.590
