00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:37.780
Ugh, I'm so pissed!

00:07:37.780 --> 00:07:40.720
That piece of shit! I hope 
you guys are prepared!

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:43.470
What does... "kill" mean?

00:07:42.020 --> 00:07:45.980 line:20%
I'm going to sue the hell out of 
you guys! This is unbelievable!

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:45.980
What does... "piece of shit" mean?

00:07:46.570 --> 00:07:48.070
Would you like to learn some more?

00:07:48.070 --> 00:07:49.960
Okay, pay close attention.

00:07:49.960 --> 00:07:53.980
This is Mr. Lion. He's the king of beasts.

00:07:53.980 --> 00:07:55.620
