00:07:55.620 --> 00:07:57.670
and the one with the long 
neck is Mr. Giraffe.

00:07:57.670 --> 00:08:00.160
The one eating the grass is Mr. Zebra.

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:01.500
And...

00:08:02.020 --> 00:08:03.410
Oh, what's this?

00:08:03.410 --> 00:08:06.540
This is what "kill" means. 
Do you understand?

00:08:06.540 --> 00:08:09.420
It means to make them die, 
or to get rid of them.

00:08:09.910 --> 00:08:13.380
Next... Oh, we have some children's games.

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:16.510
A spinning top and baseball.

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:20.100
This is bowling, and these are ice skates.

00:08:22.340 --> 00:08:26.230
Oh, dear! Look at how handy these things 
are when you use them like this!

00:08:26.450 --> 00:08:28.680
The ones who died are the pieces of shit.

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:33.200
You use "piece" when there's only one and 
say "pieces" when there's more than one.

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:34.560
Do you understand?

00:08:34.560 --> 00:08:38.330
But you can kill them in whatever 
way your instincts tell you to.

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:42.670
However, you are forbidden 
to attack this girl named Trish.

00:08:42.670 --> 00:08:44.290
You need to capture her alive.

00:08:44.290 --> 00:08:47.760
There is also a newbie
whose face we haven't seen yet.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:52.130
They're with Bucciarati as well, 
so you need to find them and kill them.

00:08:52.150 --> 00:08:54.290 position:20%
I have to pee.
What should I do?

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:56.350
What should you do?

00:08:56.860 --> 00:08:58.660
I mean, just do it?

00:08:58.660 --> 00:09:00.920
Babies pee all the time.

00:09:00.920 --> 00:09:03.980
But it doesn't look like 
the lock's been broken...

00:09:03.980 --> 00:09:05.880
H-Hey, what is this?!

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:09.060
There's something leaking from 
the ceiling of this stupid train!

00:09:09.060 --> 00:09:10.820
I don't see anything...

00:09:11.650 --> 00:09:13.030
I-It stinks!

00:09:13.030 --> 00:09:16.070
What is this?! It's so dirty and gross!

00:09:16.070 --> 00:09:17.240
Miss...

00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:23.820 position:20%
Mommy said that I stink.
