that make you feel about her?

00:09:24.310 --> 00:09:26.280
What a great mommy!

00:09:25.290 --> 00:09:26.280 line:20%
Yes!

00:09:26.290 --> 00:09:28.680
Di molto! This is extremely wonderful!

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:30.250
You're learning so well!

00:09:30.270 --> 00:09:32.240 position:20%
I'm hungry...
What should I do?

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:37.110
Not yet. You haven't learned enough yet.

00:09:37.110 --> 00:09:38.030
It's too soon.

00:09:38.030 --> 00:09:39.500
Let me drink! Hurry and let me drink!

00:09:39.830 --> 00:09:42.220
Hey, not yet! I told you, not yet!

00:09:42.220 --> 00:09:43.930
I can't take this anymore!

00:09:43.930 --> 00:09:46.170
I can't spend another second on this train!

00:09:46.170 --> 00:09:49.610
I'll sue the train company and make sure 
they take responsibility for all this!

00:09:49.610 --> 00:09:52.800
I'll tell them the bump on my 
head is a concussion, too...

00:09:59.580 --> 00:10:01.780
Huh? I don't hear her anymore...

00:10:04.990 --> 00:10:07.220
She was too good of a mother!

00:10:07.220 --> 00:10:12.590
It's good that she taught him the desire 
to kill first, but this is too early!

00:10:15.640 --> 00:10:16.550
H-Hey!

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:22.130 position:20%
Bucciarati's DNA is currently not moving...
