00:10:53.500 --> 00:10:55.170
That's true.

00:10:55.170 --> 00:10:57.390
Fugo's got a good point.

00:10:57.390 --> 00:11:00.090
Then let's hear what 
Bucciarati wants us to do.

00:11:02.050 --> 00:11:04.000
Wh-What are you doing, Giorno?

