Let's make the closet a toilet.

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:26.660
Please, go ahead.

00:12:26.660 --> 00:12:27.830
Go ahead?

00:12:27.830 --> 00:12:30.270
You said you had to go to the bathroom.

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:35.500
I don't know where it leads underneath that, 
but I'm sure the turtle will be fine.

00:12:35.500 --> 00:12:36.980
It might actually get nutrients from it.

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:41.860
I have no idea what you're trying to say...

00:12:42.470 --> 00:12:44.980
Bucciarati, we've procured a car.

00:12:45.340 --> 00:12:47.950
All right. Once we confirm 
that we're safe, let's head out.

00:12:47.950 --> 00:12:49.290
Understood.

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:57.560
That bike... When did it show up here?

00:12:57.560 --> 00:12:59.040
Where's the person who was riding it?

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:01.240
Giorno, is something wrong?

00:13:05.050 --> 00:13:06.050
Trish?

00:13:20.100 --> 00:13:21.610
What the hell?!

00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:23.560
Trish!

00:13:24.700 --> 00:13:26.250
I-Impossible!

00:13:27.610 --> 00:13:28.610
Trish!

00:13:28.910 --> 00:13:29.580
Zipper—

