Don't tell me... Bucciarati!

00:13:54.590 --> 00:13:56.690
Where's Trish? Trish!

00:13:56.690 --> 00:13:59.620
I had the turtle in my 
hands this whole time...

00:13:59.620 --> 00:14:01.920
I'd know if they came outside.

