it the moment it attacks me?

00:15:58.770 --> 00:16:01.730
Where is it hiding, and how is 
it carving out pieces of me?

00:16:01.730 --> 00:16:04.050
Carving out pieces... Which means...

00:16:05.690 --> 00:16:07.480
Shpang

00:16:07.480 --> 00:16:09.960
So you've carved away his leg and eye, too?

00:16:09.960 --> 00:16:14.200
Di molto! Well done! 
Now, come back, Babyhead!

00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:16.530 position:20%
The attack was unsuccessful.
Obviously, he's figured out what I am. What should I do?

00:16:17.460 --> 00:16:18.980
What?

00:16:19.600 --> 00:16:20.990
<font size="19">The newbie outside has removed the key from the turtle's back.</c>

00:16:20.990 --> 00:16:22.990
<font size="19">Apparently, when someone removes the key, only living things can leave.</c>

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:25.330 position:20%
My body is floating upward.
What should I do?

00:16:25.330 --> 00:16:29.510
I'm not sure what you're 
saying... Living things?

00:16:29.510 --> 00:16:33.050
You're a Stand! It doesn't matter 
if you're living or not.

00:16:33.050 --> 00:16:35.430 position:20%
That's true, but right now,
I have the eye that I stole from him.
His eye is living.

00:16:38.120 --> 00:16:40.980
I knew it... It was that cabinet.

00:16:51.550 --> 00:16:52.880
I see now...

00:16:53.580 --> 00:16:55.720
It's not that I couldn't see the enemy.

00:16:55.720 --> 00:16:57.890
I'd seen them all along!

00:16:57.890 --> 00:17:02.910
This ability chops up humans and 
reconstructs them into something else!

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:04.620 position:20%
Melone.
What should I do?
What should I do?
What should I do?

00:17:04.620 --> 00:17:08.720
Don't panic! Who cares if he 
figured out your ability?

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:12.260
The newbie hasn't been able to breathe for 
a while, and he's missing a leg, right?

00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:16.050
Just defeat him already and steal 
the turtle, along with Trish!

00:17:16.050 --> 00:17:16.970
Roger.

00:17:19.020 --> 00:17:20.390
Golden Wind!

00:17:24.400 --> 00:17:26.500
It's dodging by splitting itself apart!

00:17:26.500 --> 00:17:27.730
Which means...

00:17:39.410 --> 00:17:40.990
G-Guys...

00:17:41.550 --> 00:17:43.580
I need to somehow... let them know...

00:17:47.310 --> 00:17:48.250
That had some effect!

00:17:48.250 --> 00:17:50.880
No, that was just a rock.

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:58.220
Sh-Shit...

00:17:58.220 --> 00:18:00.190
Trish is going to get taken...

00:18:00.190 --> 00:18:03.430
At this rate, Bucciarati will be eliminated!

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:08.540
I-It's strong...

00:18:09.110 --> 00:18:11.860
Is it... invincible?

00:18:26.210 --> 00:18:28.750
I will leave the newbie's corpse here.

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:34.670
As planned, I've quietly captured Trish.

00:18:34.670 --> 00:18:36.630
Di molto! Good!

00:18:39.110 --> 00:18:43.180
I'm heading back to the train 
you're on now, Melone.

00:18:47.450 --> 00:18:50.890
Reconstructing humans into objects...

00:18:50.890 --> 00:18:55.000
Your ability gave me an excellent hint.

00:18:55.610 --> 00:18:59.660
Your ability is similar to my Golden Wind.

00:19:01.290 --> 00:19:04.990
They're very much alike in the way 
that they both recreate something.

00:19:05.440 --> 00:19:10.360
Due to the hint you gave me, 
and almost being killed,

00:19:10.360 --> 00:19:11.820
it would appear...

00:19:12.490 --> 00:19:14.430
that I've grown a little.

00:19:15.390 --> 00:19:17.970
M-Melone, did you hear that?

00:19:18.410 --> 00:19:23.410
I totally forgot earlier, but now 
I know the newbie's Stand ability.

00:19:23.410 --> 00:19:24.970
What about the newbie?

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:33.980 line:20%
His button has become an eye! 
In his hand! It became an eyeball!

00:19:30.370 --> 00:19:33.240
Hey, Babyhead, what are you talking about?

00:19:33.240 --> 00:19:35.020
What's this about the dead newbie?

00:19:35.020 --> 00:19:38.130
He inserted the eye into his face!

00:19:35.020 --> 00:19:39.020
<c.colord29d68>Rum</c><c.colorcf626a>ble</c>

00:19:38.130 --> 00:19:40.320
He did the same with his throat and leg!

00:19:40.320 --> 00:19:42.660
His ability is to create life!

00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:44.940
He created his own parts!

00:19:44.940 --> 00:19:46.910
His ability is the exact opposite of mine!

00:19:46.910 --> 00:19:49.410
Hey, who the hell are you talking about?

00:19:50.380 --> 00:19:53.210
You're not getting away! Golden Wind!

00:19:54.630 --> 00:19:56.960
The newbie... He...

00:19:57.360 --> 00:19:59.260
He's been revived!

00:20:01.150 --> 00:20:03.470
A-Are you listening, Melone?

00:20:03.470 --> 00:20:07.080
He made parts of the motorcycle into roots!

00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:08.360
I can't separate them!

00:20:08.360 --> 00:20:10.510
I have to get rid of the 
parts that are stuck!

00:20:10.510 --> 00:20:12.830
I need to get away from the bike!

00:20:23.170 --> 00:20:25.930
Did it turn into a rock again?

00:20:26.740 --> 00:20:28.960
This isn't good. He's going 
to try to pick up the turtle.

00:20:28.960 --> 00:20:31.330
I'll kill him before he picks it up!

00:20:31.330 --> 00:20:33.370
Calm down, Babyhead!

00:20:33.370 --> 00:20:35.590
Let him pick up the turtle.

00:20:35.590 --> 00:20:37.240
What do you mean?

00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:42.090
The moment he picks up the turtle, 
tear him apart for good.

00:20:42.090 --> 00:20:44.430
Oil's pouring out. That's not good!

00:20:44.780 --> 00:20:47.720
Make sure he can never get up again!

00:20:57.850 --> 00:20:59.090
I got him!

00:20:59.900 --> 00:21:04.040
It was only a little bit, but how 
dare you freak me out, you bastard?!

00:21:04.040 --> 00:21:06.470
Now, I'm going to rip your head—

00:21:06.470 --> 00:21:11.410
I've learned a lot from your ability 
to turn humans into objects.

00:21:12.270 --> 00:21:16.980
I'm not sure if it's fate or if our 
Stands were attracted to each other

00:21:16.980 --> 00:21:19.040
due to their similarities that we met.

00:21:19.040 --> 00:21:23.590
But because of you, 
my Golden Wind was able to grow.

00:21:23.590 --> 00:21:25.620
Wh-Where did it go?

00:21:25.620 --> 00:21:28.680
I just tore off your wrist. Where did it go?

00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:30.620
Tore off?

00:21:30.620 --> 00:21:32.070
That's incorrect.

00:21:32.550 --> 00:21:34.900
I intentionally let it go.

00:21:34.900 --> 00:21:37.480
I'd like to give you a little advice.

00:21:37.480 --> 00:21:43.520
You should probably use your hand to 
defend yourself, rather than attack me.

00:21:43.520 --> 00:21:46.070
D-Don't you dare underestimate me!

00:21:46.070 --> 00:21:47.110
Take this!

00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:49.390
What?!

00:21:50.770 --> 00:21:55.020
The hand that I cut off has already 
become another living creature

00:21:55.020 --> 00:21:56.750
and invaded your body.

00:21:57.750 --> 00:21:58.560
Yes.

00:22:02.120 --> 00:22:04.460
As you can see, it turned into a piranha!

00:23:37.140 --> 00:23:40.790
Episodio 18
Head to Venice!